name: iOS Support Jet File
summary: Learn about .JETKEY files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: JETKEY files are stored in the Macintosh HD/​System/​iOSSupport/​System/​Jet directory. You should not delete or edit your system's JETKEY file.

description: A JETKEY file is a system file used by macOS devices. It contains data used to support iOS apps and devices.

instructions: JETKEY files are not meant to be opened.
